  "summary": "This EIP proposes a standard interface for non-transferable, multi-owner Soulbound tokens. Previous account-bound token standards face the issue of users losing their account keys or having them rotated, thereby losing their tokens in the process. This EIP provides a solution to this issue that allows for the recycling of SBTs.",
